 depending\nonly on the K\\\"ahler class of $\\Sigma$ and the first Chern class of $\\L$ is\nobtained.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Aug 2017 16:13:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-26"}
