C collections, while providing strong baseline results for future\nstudies over Arabic tweets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Aug 2017 06:12:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 21 Aug 2017 10:13:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-22"}
