s in\nplasma with moderate $\\beta_{\\rm p}$ provide more efficient pre-acceleration.\nThe relevance of our results to the physics of fully three-dimensional systems\nis discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Aug 2017 07:43:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-04"}
