os: a characteristic dependence on the early stage equation of\nstate is observed. The enhancement of both the elliptic and the transverse\nradial flow and the simultaneous collapse of the directed flow of nucleons\noffers a clear signature if 1.O.P.T. is realized at the highest baryon\ndensities created in high energy heavy-ion collisions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Aug 2017 14:04:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-04"}
